column5: I am looking at new boats, I have come across a 178 Ultracraft with a full windshield.  They are made by Misty River, and very well priced. It has a Double hull, and all thickness are thicker than a Alumacraft I have been looking at. Looks like a very solid durable boat.  Just wondering if anyone has an experience with these boats.  Will come with a 115 ETEC.  thanks  Bryan
no one own one of these things????????
